  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Innovation Node: Sustainable Manufacturing 2016</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">(1) focus policy attention on issues of strategic technological importance for both countries; (2) building policy consensus and  foundation for in-depth cooperation; (3) sharing lessons and insight on tools and methods for strategy and practice within a particular industrial sector/ key engineering theme; (4) reach policy positions to advocate for legistlative change</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Innovation Nodes are a bilateral forum for senior Engineer-to-Engineer dialogues around areas of significant development priority to share knowledge and build policy consensus on the professional level and advocate for reform on policy and practice. Nodes focus attention on issues, laying the foundation for activity planning and network building thereafter.</narrative>
  </description>
